{"tid":463931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小學雞-寶物大典故","createTime":"2017-11-10T04:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T08:37:04.000Z","uid":99819,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7f44e68e9de1e7b3670d0edaea32377afd25e258","tid":463931,"uid":99819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/115053_26cfa3be36bb563d7b4599a62a966012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F115053_26cfa3be36bb563d7b4599a62a966012.jpg&h=2c623b78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有機關嘅筆盒，細細個好羨慕坐隔離個小學雞有依一款嘅筆盒，一個筆盒真係可以玩成堂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/115329_850f58a307b3cd7c0b7d290a288ff286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F115329_850f58a307b3cd7c0b7d290a288ff286.jpg&h=01850306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文具店價值＄100嘅小學雞拉一下打一下手槍，細個拎出街玩個個當你神咁拜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/115624_5532ee83a060601e0324903de618b8a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F115624_5532ee83a060601e0324903de618b8a5.jpg&h=e875545d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超人襟章魷魚絲，買返屋企唔係因為想食魷魚絲，而係想要個襟章天日同人大戰三百個回合，夢寐以求想抽超人，點知係怪獸，仲要鬥輸左比人，連個襟章都無撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/120144_588b5c11bc88c7eee6cbd8b6d08820b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F120144_588b5c11bc88c7eee6cbd8b6d08820b6.jpg&h=7145b5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手摺激鬥戰車，鑽研唔同嘅樣，一定要靚過人地果架，之後又大戰三百回合。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668c6ca018681ffbdab3d5abf9bee9eef43260a2","tid":463931,"uid":99819,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/122006_1aac2d9eee8fe762513c9b5aa410a651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F122006_1aac2d9eee8fe762513c9b5aa410a651.jpg&h=a979f9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小學雞摺爪，十隻手指都摺晒，之後去攻擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec77892b9db95f6721cac61e15603126348188d","tid":463931,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"超人襟章贏左就可以攞埋輸嘅襟章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b532d70af3f3a6ebe94cf85963815336d316bd69","tid":463931,"uid":50830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/124823_f3449ec88c04804fef824de1d1ccac72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F124823_f3449ec88c04804fef824de1d1ccac72.jpg&h=d53bbeb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"553f5b480b2593de0328c469b1a7a2a1ca8e4acd","tid":463931,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"細細個無錢我朋友成日買超人魷魚絲比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13321b639e41c8324b477a0fd8cf65dc0c48ea2f","tid":463931,"uid":99819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/124823_f3449ec88c04804fef824de1d1ccac72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F124823_f3449ec88c04804fef824de1d1ccac72.jpg&h=d53bbeb7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n奇趣圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，可惜我無玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24213637bef9cedb3efc